              <div class="ya-row-body">
                <div class="ya-row-label move">The move</div>
                <p>A purpose-built pilgrimage product: <strong>darshan and queue bookings</strong>, verified stays near the temple, <strong>group coordination</strong> for families travelling together, and Scapia Coins that mean something on a route people take every single year.</p>
