              <div class="ya-row-body">
                <div class="ya-row-label grow">Why it compounds</div>
                <p>Pilgrimage is repeat, seasonal, and deeply word-of-mouth. One trusted family brings the next ten. It is the <strong>lowest-cost door</strong> into exactly the customer the Series C is chasing.</p>
