              <div class="ya-row-body">
                <div class="ya-row-label move">The move</div>
                <p>Re-centre the product on the first-timer: <strong>vernacular, plain-language onboarding</strong>, a guided "your first flight" walkthrough from booking to boarding, <strong>domestic value</strong> front and centre instead of international forex, and a lounge made to feel welcoming rather than intimidating.</p>
