              <div class="ya-row-body">
                <div class="ya-row-label grow">Why it compounds</div>
                <p>Win someone's first journey and you own every journey after it. It is the <strong>cheapest, stickiest loyalty</strong> there is, and it is invisible to competitors fighting over frequent flyers.</p>
              </div>
